name: Angry Birds
tagline: Another Angry Birds Mock for iOS
body:
### Welcome to my game!

This is my Angry Birds mock game made for iOS 7 using SpriteBuilder and the Cocos2D framework. The project includes the SpriteBuilder project and it's ready to use! Enjoy!

![Splash Screen](http://s28.postimg.org/jgfpoys7h/Captura_de_pantalla_de_Simulador_i_OS_9_8_2014_23.png)

![Screenshot 1](http://s16.postimg.org/p5aqj3cv9/Captura_de_pantalla_de_Simulador_i_OS_9_8_2014_23.png)

![Level Selector](http://s16.postimg.org/xuc4f4dlx/Captura_de_pantalla_de_Simulador_i_OS_10_8_2014_0.png)

![Screenshot 2](http://s17.postimg.org/lmextxlyn/Captura_de_pantalla_de_Simulador_i_OS_10_8_2014_0.png)

> Inspired by Angry Birds
> https://www.angrybirds.com/play/angry-birds
